### CampusMarket - User Reports
### Prerequisite: backend started with -Dspring-boot.run.profiles=seed

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@userToken = mock-1001-USER
@adminToken = mock-9001-ADMIN

### Submit product report as USER
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/reports
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "targetType": "product",
  "targetId": 3001,
  "targetLabel": "Advanced Math Review Pack",
  "reason": "inaccurate_content",
  "content": "The product description appears inconsistent with the preview."
}

### Submit report without token - expect 401
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/reports
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "targetType": "product",
  "targetId": 3001,
  "reason": "inaccurate_content",
  "content": "Anonymous reports are not accepted."
}

### Submit report with invalid targetType - expect business error
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/reports
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "targetType": "unknown",
  "targetId": 3001,
  "reason": "inaccurate_content",
  "content": "Invalid target type should be rejected."
}

### Admin can see submitted reports
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/reports?status=pending
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Admin processes a report
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/reports/6001/process
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "resolved",
  "resolution": "Verified and recorded by admin."
}
